Package: ctw
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Command-line toolkit for Twitter v2 API
 A Go-based CLI tool for working with Twitter v2 REST endpoints.
 .
 Features include:
  * Filtered stream and search capabilities
  * User lookup and relationship management
  * Tweet operations (create, delete, lookup)
  * Media upload with chunked transfer
  * Direct messages
  * Likes, retweets, and bookmarks
  * Timeline access
